^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The best way for Margaret to play the hand is to realize that her only entries to dummy are in trump and she needs to take lots of minor suit finesses. So she should play a heart honor from her hand and overtake with the @HA. Take the Diamond finesse. If that wins, she is home free, as she only loses 1 club trick at most. |
