NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Someone asked me if Margaret should double rather than bidding 2@H. She certainly has a good enough heart suit, and is good enough to double and correct. Doubling and correcting would be correct had she chosen to do it and it might even work out best. However, the argument for bidding 2@H is that, if partner raises, she has an easy 4@H bid. And 4@H rates to be the most likely game her side can make. |
